        <updateDate>2021-05-25T14:21:38Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Community Broadband Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits states from blocking the provision of broadband by public providers, public-private partnership providers, or cooperatively organized providers. Further, public providers and state or local entities participating in a partnership must administer applicable ordinances and rules without discrimination against competing private providers.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
